AP McCoy finished third on Box Office in his last-ever race at Sandown Park on Saturday . 
  The 20-time champion jockey was reduced to tears after the race . 
  McCoy described the final day of his career as 'the hardest day' of his life . 
  He finished third in the Bet365 Handicap Hurdle . 
  McCoy said he hopes someone will break his record . 
 